steps.step: {"blocks":[{"key":"1jeq3","text":"Place 50 µm thick brain slices in a jar (or well). The jar or well should be able to hold ~2-5 ml Phosphate Buffered Saline (PBS) for proper washing.","type":"align-justify","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"50pak","text":" ","type":"atomic","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[{"key":0,"offset":0,"length":1}],"data":{}},{"key":"55bns","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"e5hu7","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"4c8l5","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{"0":{"type":"notes","mutability":"IMMUTABLE","data":{"blocks":[{"data":{},"depth":0,"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"90mtp","text":"The volume of solutions specified in this protocol are recommended for a maximum of 12 slices. If using more slices than 12, it is suggested to increase the preincubation volume to 2 ml and the incubation for primary and secondary antibodies to 1.5 ml.","type":"align-justify"}],"entityMap":{}}}}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"apkgo","text":"Place the jar or well on an orbital shaker for ~10-15 mins. ","type":"align-justify","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"daot9","text":" ","type":"atomic","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[{"key":0,"offset":0,"length":1}],"data":{}},{"key":"29vfg","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{"0":{"type":"notes","mutability":"IMMUTABLE","data":{"blocks":[{"data":{},"depth":0,"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[{"length":87,"offset":90,"style":"bold"}],"key":"1j78t","text":"Shaker speed should be sufficient for the slices to move but not damage from the shaking. Be careful not to damage the slices or leave them dry without any buffer for too long. ","type":"align-justify"}],"entityMap":{}}}}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"e9m6k","text":"Prepare preincubation solution containing PBS with 10% Normal Bovine Serum (NBS) and 0.5% Triton-X (total 1.5 ml per well/jar) during the last wash.","type":"align-justify","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"df234","text":"Remove the PBS from the last wash and add the preincubation solution. ","type":"align-justify","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"em53l","text":" ","type":"atomic","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[{"key":0,"offset":0,"length":1}],"data":{}},{"key":"2a2ul","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{"0":{"type":"notes","mutability":"IMMUTABLE","data":{"blocks":[{"data":{},"depth":0,"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[{"length":96,"offset":0,"style":"bold"}],"key":"3c3n9","text":"Make sure all slices are in the solution and freely moving (e.g. not stuck to side of well/jar).","type":"align-justify"}],"entityMap":{}}}}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"51ibo","text":"Add the Primary Antibody to the above mix in the desired concentration. For instance, the S100β and ChAT antibodies were used at 1:1000 and 1:100, respectively. ","type":"align-justify","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}
{"blocks":[{"key":"dct6v","text":"Remove all the Primary Antibody Solution and add fresh PBS.","type":"align-justify","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"3amfn","text":"Prepare PBS with 2% Normal Bovine Serum (NBS) and 0.4% Triton-X (total 1 ml per well/jar) during the last wash. ","type":"align-justify","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"5pba7","text":"Add the Secondary Antibody to the above mix in the desired concentration (commonly 1:300). For instance, Donkey anti-Guinea pig Alexa Fluor 488 and Donkey anti-Goat Dylight 594 were used at 1:300. ","type":"align-justify","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"3rh2u","text":"Once done, remove all the PBS from the last wash and add the Secondary Antibody Solution. ","type":"align-justify","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"eta39","text":" ","type":"atomic","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[{"key":0,"offset":0,"length":1}],"data":{}},{"key":"feupd","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{"0":{"type":"notes","mutability":"IMMUTABLE","data":{"blocks":[{"data":{},"depth":0,"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[{"length":96,"offset":0,"style":"bold"}],"key":"20squ","text":"Make sure all slices are in the solution and freely moving (e.g. not stuck to side of well/jar).","type":"align-justify"}],"entityMap":{}}}}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"8jpf6","text":"Leave to incubate for ~2-5 h at room temperature on an orbital shaker.","type":"align-justify","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"as20k","text":"Prepare DAPI solution by mixing 1 µl DAPI Readymade solution in 1 ml PB (1:1000). ","type":"align-justify","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}
{"blocks":[{"key":"cm4q4","text":"Remove the PB from the last wash and add the DAPI Solution.","type":"align-justify","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}
{"blocks":[{"key":"e9m0r","text":"Remove all the DAPI Solution and add fresh PB. ","type":"align-justify","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"94c21","text":"Add nail polish to the edges to seal the Vectashield shut and leave to dry before long-term storage in the fridge.","type":"align-justify","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"ba8r7","text":" ","type":"atomic","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[{"key":0,"offset":0,"length":1}],"data":{}},{"key":"bor5f","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{"0":{"type":"notes","mutability":"IMMUTABLE","data":{"blocks":[{"data":{},"depth":0,"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"c3p2b","text":"Proceed with imaging within days after completing the protocol.
